{"id": 437, "genre": 1001, "title": "糟糕的约会地点，你受不了哪个？", "description": "没对象也可以积累的理论知识，还不拿本儿来抄？！", "record_count": 2695, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183549ewHTRrxjQnZoUdza.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-22T11:53:22Z", "options": [{"id": 4398, "content": "所以哪里好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4400, "content": "随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65049}, {"id": 4401, "content": "只能去开房了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129868}, {"id": 4405, "content": "厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39499}, {"id": 4147, "content": "商场，没完没了的买买买，心（钱包）累", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4149, "content": "还没买到合适的遮肉泳衣，男朋友约我去游泳", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4150, "content": "夏天去公园散步，差点被蚊子吃掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4151, "content": "唱歌跑调的人才懂在KTV约会的心酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4152, "content": "旅游景点，规划行程的时候我们就分手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4148, "content": "想好好聊聊却去了不方便讲话的电影院", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4354, "content": "网吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 464, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146040}, {"id": 4355, "content": "人山人海需要排队的饭店，好不容易坐进去，向对面说话基本靠吼", "image": null, "praise_count": 427, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141305}, {"id": 4356, "content": "没有最糟糕的约会地点，只有最糟糕的约会对象…", "image": null, "praise_count": 400, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142518}, {"id": 4357, "content": "肯德基麦当劳——敢情你是在和网友见面吗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65078}, {"id": 4384, "content": "行为艺术现场。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 4388, "content": "听你们说完，好像只有去开房了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146166}, {"id": 4379, "content": "到处是人的 shopping mall", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 4416, "content": "照你们这么来，只能去火星了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146279}, {"id": 4678, "content": "不记得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145804}, {"id": 5263, "content": "约会去超市，呵呵哒，我是要减肥的人，出来的时候两大兜零食算什么。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146065}, {"id": 5913, "content": "随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149038}, {"id": 5851, "content": "公司食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122338}, {"id": 4867, "content": "网吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147582}, {"id": 4365, "content": "人山人海人挤人，次次堵车单程一小时的市中心商业街", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 4366, "content": "【讲真】\"我带你去一西餐厅！\" 然后被带到了萨莉亚……", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125628}, {"id": 4371, "content": "有人的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 4373, "content": "KTV", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 6408}, {"id": 4374, "content": "公园 麦当劳 游乐场", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 4375, "content": "这么下去地球上没啥地方适合约会了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123663}, {"id": 4376, "content": "大排档 便利店 步行街", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 4377, "content": "巴士站 展览厅 体育馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 5916, "content": "逛街", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149110}, {"id": 6944, "content": "最坑爹的一次是\n“我带你去滑旱冰～”“好～”\n然而到了地方人家旱冰场早就搬了或关门了。。于是他把我晾了半天我该说啥。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153516}, {"id": 6945, "content": "我带你去滑旱冰        好\n然而旱冰场早就不在了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153516}, {"id": 13345, "content": "对的人哪里约会都不糟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202465}, {"id": 6179, "content": "第一次约会本该是两个人爱情故事的开始…\n现在不管是不是第一次约或是见网友百分之九十九的女性旁边都会有个闺蜜呀好友  同事之类的…     这只是其次，主要是两人处对象成不成那个谁谁谁反倒变成关键人物了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147671}, {"id": 4389, "content": "逛街", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117090}, {"id": 4390, "content": "逛街", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117090}, {"id": 4392, "content": "听你们这么说，单身挺好", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211618IjlPYC0JVGuWqKmr.jpg", "praise_count": 219, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 4394, "content": "有监控的地方..", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77525}, {"id": 6954, "content": "单身狗表示在梦里…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111492}, {"id": 4406, "content": "优衣库试衣间", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39499}, {"id": 4407, "content": "商场的楼梯间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146232}, {"id": 4414, "content": "人多的地方 会害羞", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146268}, {"id": 8520, "content": "打工发传单的地方，南京路，大学城", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164626}, {"id": 4435, "content": "人特别多的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146348}, {"id": 4438, "content": "酒吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146411}, {"id": 4448, "content": "一群人真是娇情，和谁约会才是关键。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50305}, {"id": 4461, "content": "等等", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234837X46aqLTYpQtOCvRS.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8052, "content": "感觉寒酸的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160166}]}